      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Apologies and Immediate Resolution for Your Flight Issues\n\nDear [Customer Name],\n\nWe sincerely apologize for the inconvenience you experienced with your recent flight (SL402). We understand how frustrating a delay and missed connecting flight can be, especially when it comes with unanticipated consequences like your current location and lack of accommodation.\n\nTo resolve this promptly, we have arranged for a comfortable and complimentary hotel stay in Chicago for tonight. Additionally, we are processing a full refund for the lost flight. We deeply regret any distress this has caused you and will ensure that our customer service continually improves to prevent similar issues in the future.\n\nThank you for your patience and understanding. Please don’t hesitate to reach out if you require further assistance.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]\n[Customer Service Team] \n\n[Date]",
